casebody.data:
Antonio BARSOCCHI and Bruno Bianchi, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 7147. Circuit Court, of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 8, 1933.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellee, ordered appeal in above cause dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause.
